      p The original 
        i  Maison Apothecare
        |  packaging was designed to be a modern classic, 
        |  drawing from the vintage apothecary inspiration. The dark brown
        |  bottles with the delicate shape label established 
        i  Maison Apothecare
        |  as a familiar and well-loved local brand.
      p The packaging evolved over time to include more types of products
        |  while still living under the umbrella of the established
        i  Maison Apothecare
        |  brand, modern and elegant while still giving a nod to
        |  the original apothecary influence.
    
